{
  "id": "ex_technical_383f54ae",
  "intent": "Execute magnetic bead-based cleanup of PCR amplicons using QIAact beads on 1-12 samples. Combine 20\u00b5L each of forward and reverse PCR products in deep-well magnetic plate, add 60\u00b5L nuclease-free water and 100\u00b5L magnetic beads. Perform 5-minute room temperature incubation, magnetic separation for 10 minutes, supernatant removal, dual ethanol washes with 200\u00b5L per wash, air-dry beads for 10 minutes, then elute purified DNA in 16\u00b5L nuclease-free water with final transfer of 13.4\u00b5L to PCR strip tubes.",
